<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0f1e; --accent: #fbbf24; --teal: #5eead4; --pink: #fb7185;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html, body { width: 1200px; height: 675px; overflow: hidden;
    font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "Inter", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #fff;
    background:
      radial-gradient(900px 600px at 18% 12%, rgba(94,234,212,0.20), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(800px 500px at 90% 92%, rgba(251,113,133,0.18), transparent 55%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0f1e 0%, #07091a 100%);
  }
  .frame { position: absolute; inset: 0; padding: 56px 64px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
  .top { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: center; }
  .badge {
    font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 4px; font-weight: 800;
    padding: 9px 18px; border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(94,234,212,0.1); color: var(--teal);
    border: 1px solid rgba(94,234,212,0.35);
  }
  .badge.pink { color: var(--pink); border-color: rgba(251,113,133,0.4); background: rgba(251,113,133,0.08); }

  .center { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; }
  h1 {
    font-size: 88px; line-height: 1.12; font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #c2c9dc 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  h1 .glow {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--pink));
    -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 24px rgba(251,191,36,0.5));
  }
  .sub {
    font-size: 26px; line-height: 1.6; color: #c2c9dc; font-weight: 500;
    max-width: 980px;
  }
  .sub b { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 800; }

  .bottom {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .bottom .lhs b { color: var(--teal); }
  .bottom .rhs {
    padding: 10px 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18); border-radius: 999px;
    color: #fff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
  }
</style></head>
<body>
<div class="frame">
  <div class="top">
    <span class="badge">⚡ AI × 投资</span>
    <span class="badge pink">🧵 长推</span>
  </div>
  <div class="center">
    <h1>一晚 DD 完<br><span class="glow">56 个奇绩项目</span></h1>
    <div class="sub">
      一张展区照、一篇官方文章、22 张项目卡截图。<br>
      30 分钟跑完 <b>8 维度投资级 DD</b> + <b>7 路 AI 并发调研</b> + 一键部署。
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bottom">
    <div class="lhs">2026 · 奇绩创坛春季路演 · <b>1% 录取率</b></div>
    <div class="rhs">↓ 往下翻 thread</div>
  </div>
</div>
</body></html>
